**Key notes:**
- The SDK automatically stores the session in cookies/localStorage after `createEmailPasswordSession()` succeeds
- `ID.unique()` generates a unique user ID (you can also provide your own)
- You must enable Email/Password auth in your Appwrite project settings
- The session persists across page reloads until you call `deleteSession()` or it expires

